/*
Description : This is a Java Program that shows if a set of documents 
are about the same topic or not.
the program will scan the words of the documents and check if
there are common words between the documents which should then 
declare that these documents are similar.
stop words for example like the , a , of , he etc should be excluded
from the analysis.

